Description:
The overall aims and objectives are for the NHS to deliver a digital staff passport service to meet the needs of two main user cases: 
(a)	the rotational movements of Doctors in Training (both permanent changes in employment and through lead employer arrangements) and;
(b)	temporary staff movements of any NHS staff member.

Advice regarding our proposals for funding companies' bioresources activities at PR24. 

This will involve:
•	gaining a deep understanding of our proposals; 
•	quality assuring our proposals, e.g. assessing any key risks or gaps in our approach and where our approach looks defensible; 
•	identifying measures to strengthen our proposals; 
•	where appropriate, identifying alternative options to our proposals; 
•	drafting of key text to help explain and justify the approach we will put forward in our draft methodology.
